</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n板橋區係新北市核心<br />\n而新莊區係新北市政府主力發展既副核心地帶 所以叫副都心 當然某程度上都係想學日本咁規劃喇"},{"pid":"c4813cb8818bd1c04c4b30969acff9c59dfa28a3","tid":19092,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:50:23.000Z","msg":"台北捷運 真係好過  MTR <br />\n<br />\n班次真心準 同 密<br />\nd 站位置方便 <br />\n雖然多站,  但其實係切合需要<br />\n同埋 , 唔算貴"},{"pid":"dd4b595d351c94342b69b6f3f1bfdce33354dc56","tid":19092,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:53:00.000Z","msg":"台灣:  「未來通車試運時，首月將讓乘客免費試搭，第2個月則有半價優惠。」<br />\n<br />\n香港:「屌,  開通左當然要賺撚到你盡啦。 嗱依家講定幾錢先,  搭唔搭尤得你啦死窮鬼。 開通初期有運作問題好撚正常喎,  唔好以為唔駛畀錢搭車呀, 試搭唔撚係搭呀 ? 」"},{"pid":"82b068eb28329a9715d0289efc456f1d60edeab6","tid":19092,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:55:26.000Z","msg":"終於通車 有多一個選擇　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前往返機場都係搭的士<br />\n<br />\n一程就已經冇左張一千蚊紙　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4e1516a9864fc9f0a5eeb29c423fa7f3f0f737","tid":19092,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:56:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁多個站？機場出台北車站要幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有快車有慢車<br />\n快車4個站/37分鐘<br />\n慢車12個站/70分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.tymetro.com.tw/images2/pic/pic3102.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tymetro.com.tw%2Fimages2%2Fpic%2Fpic3102.jpg&h=14fd6ff7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n坐國光客運先9個字到咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下下拎客運同捷運比 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n你唔計埋班次, 車費, 架車臭唔臭, 落腳點方唔方便既因素 ?"},{"pid":"7ab846547d0d7b0ccb0b15baab9c0392e09b7a43","tid":19092,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:56:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>終於通車 有多一個選擇　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前往返機場都係搭的士<br />\n<br />\n一程就已經冇左張一千蚊紙　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁富貴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e00364e13c29ecf51d79ef05baf7696e1376892","tid":19092,"uid":18363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:59:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>終於通車 有多一個選擇　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前往返機場都係搭的士<br />\n<br />\n一程就已經冇左張一千蚊紙　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以選擇高鐵<br />\n160+30 台幣<br />\n30分鐘內一定到"},{"pid":"db798d92313c8e93429965de2e8291937bc0faa7","tid":19092,"uid":15,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:59:51.000Z","msg":"留名睇又延遲, btw 國光都係9個字-1個鐘, 搭慢車不如搭國光, 又有位坐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23307c20bd787cb51c2aaec638a95463002a2bd","tid":19092,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:01:00.000Z","msg":"真係通撚左先講，不停話出年通出拿通講撚左好撚多年，由佢咩都無到起好曬而家都未通。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a71c87f8c7ce170bcf86f827d13b579f412639b7","tid":19092,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:06:02.000Z","msg":"香港人 乜然都要快 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n但人地條捷運唔係為你地香港人服務架囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貼地少少啦"},{"pid":"ee8c4d80171f14d68ec52d85cb74798832b89dd0","tid":19092,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:42:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係通撚左先講，不停話出年通出拿通講撚左好撚多年，由佢咩都無到起好曬而家都未通。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n12年我去台灣已經講話起緊好快通車<br />\n16年我再去屌呀仲話起緊未通車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449b31823224541a43e551a2d283e424e0fe5e6f","tid":19092,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T03:03:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人 乜然都要快 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n但人地條捷運唔係為你地香港人服務架囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貼地少少啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台灣人都屌左好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341ecb316ccd0858d6abd36cd5f845e743c6742b","tid":19092,"uid":2867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T03:08:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人 乜然都要快 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n但人地條捷運唔係為你地香港人服務架囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貼地少少啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係連香港人都屌 依個先係問題 <br />\n出comment之前用下腦<br />\n香港人得閒都理下高鐵啦<br />\n<br />\n台灣機鐵問題好似講左十年架啦"}]}